    T - Type the Filter should be applied to.

      • mergeResults

        default FilterResult mergeResults(FilterResult res1,
                                  FilterResult res2)
        Defines how the new and old result are merged when executing a FilterSet. Only override if really necessary. NOTE: failed FilterResults are passed down without being merged.
        Parameters:
        res1 - Old FilterResult.
        res2 - New FilterResult.
        Returns:
        Merged FilterResult.
